measurements.description:
Fourteen flowers on an approximately 165-cm inflorescence; inflorescence axillary, arranged around 25-cm hoop multiple times, largest leaf 40.5cm x 3.4cm,
	six leaves on blooming pseudobulb, pseudobulb 10.2cm tall, 7cm circumference, three pseudobulbs total; sepals chestnut edged yellow; petals yellow, chestnut centrally;
	lip yellow, edged chestnut, prominent callus cream, sidelobes cream, purple marking on underside; column yellow proximally, chestnut distally; substance firm; texture waxy.
